到了警示义务，酌定对于安某死亡的损害承担30%的赔偿责任。 安某所在中学已经对其旷课、逃学、翻墙等行为进行了教育，学校的围墙设置也符合相关标准，学校已经尽到教育、管理职责，对安某死亡的损害不承担责任。 你是如何看待这一判决结果的？ 电力公司为什么会承担30%责任？ 校园安全事件为何屡禁不止？其根源在哪里？如何加强安全管控才能落到实处？"},"attached_info":"Cj8Iieyc9tismfshEAMaCDY5OTI1NDc2IOKRxokGMB84mwJAC3IJNDg0Mzk1MTk3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"457 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-eefba2ac44bade854e936f6c51b03a30_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"12_1630919273.8284993","card_id":"Q_484439042","target":{"id":484439042,"title":"如何看待上海接送孩子钟点工走俏？三胎开放后育儿市场会怎么发展？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/484439042","type":"question","created":1630647113,"answer_count":121,"follower_count":483,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[200,1395,1740,2566,105508],"comment_count":12,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"9 月 1 日，上海大部分幼儿园及中小学迎来开学第一天。据悉，今年专门用于接送学生上下学的钟点工需求略增，增幅10%左右，收费略涨，即下午 3点至 6 点接送钟点工收费较去年涨了 5 元/次，每次 35-45 元。如果接送的学生家与学校路程较远，则另行协商收费。如果2人或3人拼接，收费大约 40~60 元/次，费用按人数分摊。"},"attached_info":"Cj8Iieyc9tismfshEAMaCDY5OTM1MjI4IMnmxokGMAw44wNADHIJNDg0NDM5MDQyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"429 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b464498b9f9581096b7286917351aa53.jpg?source=2044ae36"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"13_1630919273.8290606","card_id":"Q_484969513","target":{"id":484969513,"title":"学生被学校强制要求到工厂实习致残，而学校让自行与工厂协商，学生在实习期间受伤，责任该如何判定？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/484969513","type":"question","created":1630887354,"answer_count":156,"follower_count":437,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[215,13179,33022,105508,726204],"comment_count":19,"is_follow